msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite.item_boltcutter_on_fence_1.dlg.narrator"
msgid "That doesn't seem like a good idea."
msgstr "それは良い考えとは思えない。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite.item_boltcutter_on_fence_1.dlg.narrator"
msgid "The hole is big enough."
msgstr "穴はもう十分大きい。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite.item_boltcutter_on_fence_1.dlg.narrator"
msgid "There's no reason to go back."
msgstr "戻る理由はない。"

